Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin', Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.37,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought I'd head \Nto the store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:18.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:22.71,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.79,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was looking \Nforward to leaving together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.31,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to go end things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:33.84,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on the guy from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.78,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So you are a man of the sea after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:49.30,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the sins the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:53.64,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,The people of Shioshishio \Nsince long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:58.44,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire is the \Nsoul of the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:00.02,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.50,0:01:03.16,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred fire is letting us know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:07.67,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The sea and the surface should \N make their boundaries permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.44,0:01:10.75,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the surface will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.20,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The saltflake snow is just a prelude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:17.07,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Though Akari is solely up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:20.08,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,It is not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.89,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's life is her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:25.54,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:29.02,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Since long ago from the \Nbeginning of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:02.03,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Five: Hey, Sea Slug
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki's going to be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.12,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said she's not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:12.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't look like she was \Nfeeling well on the way home yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.11,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:17.97,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:41.24,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell a red-bellied sea slug \Nabout feelings you can't tell anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.82,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,it'll tell you what's going \Nto happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:49.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Green...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.21,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's a really good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.83,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,And compared to that, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.49,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something \Nabout my feelings for Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.21,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.19,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're late, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.65,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We had a huge haul this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.28,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We've been able to get a ridiculous \Nnumber of golden-eyes lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.66,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Where's everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.64,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I was late, so I had them \Ngo ahead without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.57,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:31.47,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"What"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.23,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.88,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes, I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're childhood friends, \Nand we've been together forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:51.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so he's like family...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.14,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be a sea slug for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:04:59.32,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:03.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I like him more than just \Nas a childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:07.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But if I keep on liking Hikari,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:09.56,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep becoming \Nsomeone I don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:13.29,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to be able \Nto forgive mysel—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:32.41,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:46.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you, \Nso I went back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hear anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Like about me liking Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Like about you liking Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.34,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget about that, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:05.45,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just forget about that. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.63,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.68,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't try to touch \Nme anywhere funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.15,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.04,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, take this more seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:32.02,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me if you mess up \Nduring the sports festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.33,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You smell sweaty, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.59,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get close to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:48.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get close to you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.74,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.30,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sea girl, you're stepping on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.56,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.02,Main,guy,0000,0000,0000,,I said that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.52,Saya Mart,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:03.55,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:08.43,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.32,Triangle - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:16.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if we break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:21.99,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt Miuna-chan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.75,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You came to say that as \Nwell, right, Itaru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:27.17,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:33.08,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wrong all this time \Never since Miori-san died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.64,Always Happy - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Always Smiling \NSaya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.30,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.92,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.49,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna, you're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:53.78,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.35,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:58.20,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming by all \Nthe time, Akari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.87,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to\Ntrouble yourself though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.23,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.79,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Miuna-chan brings me happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.78,Flashback,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness'll be a hundred yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.84,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're charging me money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.68,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.65,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan is very precious to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:20.17,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wish things could \Nhave stayed that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:25.15,Flashback,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll be okay \Nif we tell her about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.49,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:29.96,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna loves you, Akari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:32.32,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, I do, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.24,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:36.18,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.29,Flashback,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.00,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,"A mistake"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.86,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say something so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:57.26,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come to break up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:01.13,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I just think we acted too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:06.41,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna likes you, too, \Nso if we just take our time—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.41,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.27,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:13.11,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You've known what needs to \Nbe done for a while, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.94,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.46,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.88,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't need to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:36.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for putting you \Nthrough so much pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.14,Go Aw,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Go Aw {M: still not completed}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sakishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:02.03,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Can you ask Uroko-sama if there was a \Nsmall girl that fell into the ocean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are yo—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan hasn't come home yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:11.75,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Her friend hasn't seen her either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.45,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.62,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.54,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that Miuna-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find Miuna for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.84,0:10:23.49,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.72,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's already late, so leave\Nthe searching to the adults...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.46,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You should be—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.92,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:29.77,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you \Ntry to act like an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:35.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never be able to replace Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:36.58,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:41.49,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So... Hurry up and go be Miuna's new mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:45.91,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.36,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed with Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:55.09,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't fall into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.96,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.13,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm hanging up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.44,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.26,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I think only the area \Nnear the mountain is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's been getting chilly at night lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, talk about a problem child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:55.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from the daughter \Nof that lecherous old ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.63,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.91,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say bad things about my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.04,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.74,Main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.70,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,your dad and everyone else \Nare really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.43,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,They're not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's{\i0} worried enough\Nto go looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.59,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:24.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:27.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we have a futon for guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:29.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna can't go to Shioshishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:38.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It is chilly at night, \Nbut it's summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:41.69,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.66,Triangle 2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Triangle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.66,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.49,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari! They said they found Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.33,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.69,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,The fishery cooperative got \Na call from Hikari-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:56.17,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,And apparently he wanted us to \Nleave everything to him for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.98,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,He really... found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.47,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.30,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.21,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I love Miuna-chan and Miori-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.49,0:13:17.78,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari dumped me, but I love him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.88,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I love you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.52,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.92,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Hikari says.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.23,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:26.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:30.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have everyone that I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:35.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I know what I should have done, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.29,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.09,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:52.25,Main,itaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give up on \Nall of us being happy either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I got some!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.15,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.36,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,This place was in business \Nuntil this spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.62,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,so the pots and plates were left as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:09.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:13.13,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki, you better make \Na better meal than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,We need to gut these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname and I will work on this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:26.04,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,so Manaka, could you go get \Nsome more fish with Miuna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:29.51,Main,Chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Hikari. This isn't nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:38.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Is this edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.96,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a sea slug?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.63,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could eat them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.45,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:50.93,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I guess red ones are really rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:53.91,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess the one the \Nother day was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.39,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Red ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:15:00.12,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat the green ones, but \Nthe red ones are for talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.07,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell it things that \Nyou can't tell anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.62,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,it'll tell you things or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.63,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.34,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.67,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can make you \Nfeel a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:15.23,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I know about something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:19.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I was \Nusing instead of a sea slug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.77,Go Aw,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,1)}Go Aw
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:19.77,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:24.19,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If you find a red one, \Nwhat will you tell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:31.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is my special \Nmiso soup, so eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:34.17,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When I find a red sea slug, \Nwhat should I tell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:34.75,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You always make this whenever \Nsomething happens, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah, I'm starting to wonder \Nif that's all you can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.45,Italics,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... what I want answers to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Then you make something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for looking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.27,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow things will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:48.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:49.99,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.68,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. S-See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty amazing, \Naren't they? The stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:05.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari's a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I know me saying that might \Nnot mean much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So don't hate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.87,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:26.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but you have all these \Npeople who love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.79,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you do. I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.54,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.42,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want there to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:49.05,Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,The way you write Miuna \Nis "beautiful ocean."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.99,Miuna,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1029,0)}Miuna
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.99,Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy loves the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:56.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If you love it, why are you \Nliving where there's land?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:00.04,Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you more, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.71,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:04.91,Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,I love, love, love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.53,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:20.84,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you \Nthink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.60,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:26.51,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's from the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.73,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:47.62,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,You smell like Mommy and Aka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.14,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:57.84,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,When Mommy died, I was full of \Nsad feelings in my stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.73,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Like I couldn't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:06.36,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Aka-chan always stayed with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.76,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,and I really started to like Aka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:13.96,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,But... when they said Aka-chan \Nmight be my new mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.10,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.99,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If Mommy... something that I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:24.44,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,if they were taken from me again, \NI wouldn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that sad feeling \Nin my stomach again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:34.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't love them, \NI wouldn't be so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,So... So I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.93,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't love them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:45.75,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't love them, \Nit won't be painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:50.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You might actually have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.67,0:18:51.67,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:56.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:19:02.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of think it might be easier \Nnot to love someone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:04.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:11.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think that it's hopeless \Nor useless to love someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:18.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have someone you love, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah... a lot of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.43,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,A lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:30.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And now I like you a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:34.13,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How long are you going \Nto hold me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:44.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a dolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:45.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Doli"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:49.66,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that people who like grade \Nschool girls are called "dolicons."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:50.75,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,From Sayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's lolicon, not dolicon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:59.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.05,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want \Nyou to help me with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.26,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.67,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,My... sea slug...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:13.06,Saya Mart,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Saya Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.82,Main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,You're early, Akari-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:13.06,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I couldn't sleep, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:29.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,My jaw hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.75,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I chewed too much gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.89,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.96,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akari! Calm do—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.55,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.58,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:48.04,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side, Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.56,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your \Nside with Miori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:53.56,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,With... Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.94,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:58.55,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I can't replace Miori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.43,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.44,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:06.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay next to you as myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.24,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.70,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So... you stay as you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:15.88,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And please... let me stay \Nby your side forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:22.46,Go Aw,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Go Away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:26.12,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, Aka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:30.80,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,They're so blue, and your \Ntears moving like waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:33.18,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,They're so pretty. They're like the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.04,0:21:35.07,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.52,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.17,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,love the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.88,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:54.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the kid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.78,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're so big, Hiradaira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:35.97,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where my strike zone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:38.14,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently today's the \Nperfect day for Tomoebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's way too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:40.10,Episode-Title - Copy,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Six: Beyond Tomoebi
